01:14:32.300 --> 01:14:35.233
because sometimes
that's all you've got.

01:14:35.233 --> 01:14:39.633
Small reminders that not
everything has gone rotten.

01:14:40.700 --> 01:14:44.167
Life's unbearable
without variety.

01:14:45.067 --> 01:14:49.367
I'd certainly hope that I
could bring something different

01:14:49.367 --> 01:14:51.700
to the people in my life.

01:14:51.700 --> 01:14:54.067
Something to inspire them.

01:14:54.067 --> 01:14:56.567
Give them something
to talk about

01:14:56.567 --> 01:14:58.700
'cause at the end of the day,

01:14:58.700 --> 01:15:01.933
that's all anyone can do,

01:15:01.933 --> 01:15:04.533
make an impression.

01:15:07.467 --> 01:15:10.400
I hope when I die

01:15:10.400 --> 01:15:14.567
people will remember
me with a smile.

01:15:18.800 --> 01:15:21.067
Clint Eastwood once said,

01:15:21.067 --> 01:15:23.733
he doesn't believe in pessimism.

01:15:23.733 --> 01:15:26.133
He said, "If something
doesn't come out"

01:15:26.133 --> 01:15:29.400
"the way you want, forge ahead."

01:15:29.400 --> 01:15:32.767
"If you think it's
gonna rain, it will."

01:15:32.767 --> 01:15:36.100
This is Warren
Thompson, signing out.

01:15:37.367 --> 01:15:42.367
(soft sad music)
